<div class="newsItem" id="sasdcommunication">
	<div class="newstitle">SASD Communications</div>
	<div class="newsbody"><p class="">In general, all “official” communication for families and the community will be released from the Superintendent’s Office and posted on our websites. Please check the websites frequently and read down through the lists of topics. On some days, there will be multiple posts regarding different topics. Please read carefully and check frequently. Information changes rapidly. Thank you for your understanding.</p></div>
